" === Tab Navigation (like <leader>l / <leader>h) ===
map <space>l nextTab
map <space>h previousTab
map <space><space> visitPreviousTab
map <space>0 firstTab
map <space>$ lastTab
map <space>p togglePinTab

" === Tab Management ===
map u restoreTab

"=== scroll up and down
map <c-u> scrollPageUp
map <c-d> scrollPageDown

" === Vomnibar (like quick open, files, search) ===
map <space>t Vomnibar.activateTabSelection

" === Browser Navigation (similar to <C-h>/<C-l>) ===
map <c-h> goBack
map <c-l> goForward
